{"title":"Spotted: Team BikeExchange riding new Giro aero road helmet at the Tour de France?","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/06/spotted-team-bikeexchange-riding-new-giro-aero-road-helmet-at-the-tour-de-france/","date":1625589891000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Hang around pro cyclists long enough, and you’re bound to spot new gear before it’s launched. There has been speculation for months that Giro’s sponsored teams have been testing a new aero road helmet, but the company’s <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GiroSportDesign\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">recent facebook posts</a> are putting the helmet in question right out in the open.</p><figure id=\"attachment_264154\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-264154\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/Giro-prototype-helmet-spotted-at-TDF-2021-photo-c-Giro-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/Giro-prototype-helmet-spotted-at-TDF-2021-photo-c-Giro-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x363/rscb20/ng:webp/ngcb20\" alt=\"New Giro aero helmet spotted at the Tour de France on Team BikeExchange riders\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/Giro-prototype-helmet-spotted-at-TDF-2021-photo-c-Giro-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/Giro-prototype-helmet-spotted-at-TDF-2021-photo-c-Giro-1-297x223.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/Giro-prototype-helmet-spotted-at-TDF-2021-photo-c-Giro-1-800x600.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb20 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06122138/G